song_lyrics: Ayodhyā Sarayūtaṭe sambhaḷāy, madhur jal tarang hālarḍu;
Chhapaiyā gām sīmāḍe gavāy, mīṭhe sūr pakṣhīnu hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 1
Sarvariyā brāhmaṇ kuḷ e Dharma-Bhaktine gṛuh mandiriye;
Īshvarno avatār thāy, choghaḍiyā chalave hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 2
Samvat aḍhāraso sāḍatrīs, chaitra sudi navmīnī rātri;
Janmyā Ghanshyām rūpe Bhagawān, felāyu ānand hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 3
Apsarā gāndharvo tyā āve, nandanvan fūlaḍe vadhāve;
Shrījīne pāraṇiye padharāve, kinnargaṇ gāye hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 4
Dev devī jāh‍navī-jaḷanī, bharī lāvī suvarṇa gāgarḍī;
Kesariyā snān karāve, gāye garve hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 5
Nar nārī bāḷ ubharāye, hīrā motīnī māḷā dharāve;
Jariyānī poshāk pe’rāve, suṇāve surīlu hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 6
Mātā Premvatī hulasāve, navratne hīnchoḷe hīnchāve;
Sohe gāve sakal sākār, Sahajānandnu hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 7
Rājā-rāṇī sant-mahant, darshane āve chhe anant;
Te to tare chhe bhavsāgar, Sahajānandnu hālaraḍu... Ayodhyā° 8
title: Ayodhyā Sarayūtaṭe sambhaḷāy
